					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "I’m not often on-call myself. By trade, I am someone who helps you build something and then runs away, and you have to live with it. I have lived through on-call rotations, and created some myself, but for the last few years I’ve been blissfully unburdened by PagerDuty and the only thing that wakes me up at night is my children."
