				"string" : "Now, [I’m no Charity Majors](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p_paJ2PB4MY) and I don’t pretend to be. You should definitely listen to her before you listen to me. [You should read the SRE workbook chapters on on-call setups](https://sre.google/workbook/on-call/) and [being on-call](https://sre.google/sre-book/being-on-call/) instead of reading my article."
